<li>Edward Strickland, "Terry Riley". <a href="/wiki/New_Grove_Dictionary_of_Music_and_Musicians" title="New Grove Dictionary of Music and Musicians" class="mw-redirect">Grove Music</a> Online <a href="http://www.grovemusic.com" class="external text" title="http://www.grovemusic.com" rel="nofollow">(subscription access)</a>.</li>
</ul>
